    Proof of concept

    Goal: use hardware concept to synthesize a preset DNA sequence. Proof is provided by sequencing. Argument according to the Design cycle: Design -> Build -> Test -> Learn -> Design (iterative)

    Sample template built using the iGEM Wiki Starter Pack by BITS Goa.

    Code released under the MIT license.

    Based on Bootstrap and themes Flatly and Darkly from Bootswatch.
